#

Easy Beef Tenderloin with Chimichurri Sauce

35 min
$20
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreePaleo

Cuisine:

AmericanArgentinian

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

BeefSteakEasyQuickGrill

Description

Juicy beef tenderloin drizzled with a vibrant and zesty chimichurri sauce, ready in just 35 minutes!

Ingredients

  • beef tenderloin: 1 pound
  • olive oil: 1/4 cup
  • red wine vinegar: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 2 cloves
  • fresh parsley: 1/4 cup
  • fresh cilantro: 1/4 cup
  • red pepper flakes: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
